<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>FAQ</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .question {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .answer {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      display: none;
    }
  </style>
  <script>
    function toggleAnswer(id) {
      var answer = document.getElementById(id);
      if (answer.style.display === "none") {
        answer.style.display = "block";
      } else {
        answer.style.display = "none";
      }
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer1')">Q: What is the purpose of this website?</div>
    <div class="answer" id="answer1">A: The purpose of this website is to provide information about our products and services.</div>
    
    <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer2')">Q: How can I contact customer support?</div>
    <div class="answer" id="answer2">A: You can contact our customer support team by phone at +123456789 or by email at support@example.com.</div>
    
    <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer3')">Q: Do you offer refunds?</div>
    <div class="answer" id="answer3">A: Yes, we offer a 30-day money-back guarantee. If you're not satisfied with your purchase, please contact our support team for a refund.</div>
    
    <div class="question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer4')">Q: How long does shipping take?</div>
    <div class="answer" id="answer4">A: Shipping times vary depending on your location. Typically, orders are delivered within 3-5 business days.</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
